About Event

​Come meet with old and new friends at the Bits in Bio Reception happening during JPM Healthcare Week in San Francisco.

Generously sponsored by Cadence Molecular Science (OpenEye) and AWS, we are excited to have you for some light appetizers and beer & wine.
